Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.02,0:02:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The time is the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.99,0:02:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Countless pirates fight\Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.20,0:02:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,the great treasure left behind\Nby Gold Roger, the Pirate King.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.79,0:03:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body\Nturned to rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.63,0:03:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,also takes to the sea\Nto become the next Pirate King.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.47,0:03:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,As Luffy and his friends\Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.51,0:03:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the World Government is less and less\Nable to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.45,0:03:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.91,0:03:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What adventure is waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.18,0:03:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.29,0:03:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.86,0:03:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Separated from the rest of the Straw Hats,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.03,0:03:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy made it to Marineford to rescue his brother, Ace, who will be executed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.84,0:03:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He got over the barricades in order\Nto make it to the scaffold with Jinbe's help
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.51,0:03:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and faced the 3 admirals!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.68,0:03:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The Whitebeards then made it to the plaza, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.15,0:03:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,An all-out battle between the Navy\Nand the Whitebeards has begun at Oris Plaza!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.25,0:03:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ice Block: Partisan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops, move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.21,0:04:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All you have is courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.38,0:04:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you're not strong enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.48,0:04:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't save him no matter how hard you try.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.82,0:04:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just get lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He is nothing but a bundle of energy who just bluffs. Young and clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.71,0:04:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But I like fools like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.05,0:05:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If I let you wreak havoc, this island won't survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.63,0:05:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why don't you protect it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on my way, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.25,0:05:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanna go further, you have to kill me first!
