Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.73,0:05:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Garp the Hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.80,0:05:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...took part in their protection!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.74,0:06:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He fought against Gold Roger, the Pirate King, 20 years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.35,0:06:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and made his name in the world—\Nhe's a legendary Navy soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.12,0:06:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that it was Garp who fought\NRoger's competitor—Shiki the Golden Lion...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.02,0:06:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...here in Marineford with Sengoku and imprisoned him in Impel Down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.27,0:06:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get tripped up by his name, you fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.74,0:06:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just an old soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.15,0:06:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd lived through that era,\Nyou should know that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.88,0:06:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...you should focus on the enemy in front of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.19,0:06:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hound Blaze!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.90,0:06:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta stop destroying the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.77,0:06:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to protect it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.64,0:07:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry and execute Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.04,0:07:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a substitute right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.91,0:07:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.55,0:07:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Make a path!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.69,0:07:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A path to rescue Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.03,0:07:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We still got those pains in the ass here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.83,0:07:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you do it, monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.50,0:07:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.94,0:07:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...the power of the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.35,0:07:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is the chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.82,0:07:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Get to the scaffold!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.19,0:07:54.66,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,How is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.09,0:07:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Not good at all! First aid won't help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:08:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He needs proper treatment!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.80,0:08:04.47,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,Straw-boy can't fight anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.47,0:08:05.84,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.52,0:08:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Fire Fist?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.09,0:08:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Gol D. Roger?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.71,0:08:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean Gold Roger?\NDid you ask me if I know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.41,0:08:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you realize why there is so much destruction in the world caused by pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.25,0:08:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all Roger's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.99,0:08:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,His fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.29,0:09:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that right before his execution,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,he bullshitted about this great treasure thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.63,0:09:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...causing the idiot pirates who believed him to run wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He should've never been born in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.07,0:09:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He was just a worthless bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.51,0:09:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after his death,\Nhe causes the pirates to roam the seas!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.88,0:09:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He's such a nuisance—living or dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.32,0:09:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He was the biggest piece of shit\Nthe world's ever seen! Remember that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's wrong? What are you getting mad for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.80,0:09:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, who are you, brat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.55,0:10:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you done in the city, Ace?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.19,0:10:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They're making a fuss over some punks\Nwho almost got killed by a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.93,0:10:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I thought they were dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?! If you cause trouble, I'm the one who'll get chewed out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.87,0:10:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you listening, Ace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.94,0:10:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly! How could he just leave\Na kid like this with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.45,0:10:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna know about Roger?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.95,0:10:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He was just a great liar and a murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes me laugh\Nthat they call him the "Pirate King!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.73,0:10:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He was more like the King of Bullshitters!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.94,0:10:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.64,0:10:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mention the name that makes me sick, brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.11,0:11:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ruining my drink! Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.41,0:11:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you looking at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.15,0:11:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing, you little shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.53,0:11:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at you! You got beaten pretty badly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.80,0:11:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ace? I heard that you're out of control these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man, you have a grandson, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.82,0:11:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he look happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.62,0:11:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're talking about Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He's growing up in fine feather!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.76,0:11:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.40,0:12:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...that I deserved to be born?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.91,0:12:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's something...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.78,0:12:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,...you'll see as you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.29,0:12:22.13,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,Carry Straw-boy to the ship in a hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.93,0:12:26.26,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,I have no choice! We gotta save Ace-boy without him...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.17,0:12:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Iva-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.07,0:12:34.10,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,You came around!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.67,0:12:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you do me a favor one last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost there! We'll be there soon, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.22,0:12:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Clear the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.79,0:12:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.97,0:13:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace-san, wait for me! I'll save you with my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.54,0:13:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We're on our way, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.45,0:13:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace, we'll save you at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.02,0:13:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for us, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.92,0:13:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.22,0:13:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! My mind is so warped! It's not the right time for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.03,0:13:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops and brother and friends are...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.80,0:13:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...going down one by one bleeding, but...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:42.17,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,Don't say "one last time!" It'll bring bad luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.44,0:13:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Can you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.78,0:13:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy and I can't stop crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.95,0:13:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,At this last moment,\NI'm starting to think that I wanna live!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.29,0:14:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you! Iva-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.00,0:14:11.20,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,Are you serious about this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.09,0:14:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He's awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.46,0:14:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.43,0:14:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so relieved!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.20,0:14:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.97,0:14:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You got frozen by Blue Pheasant and...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.38,0:14:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.35,0:14:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! It's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.95,0:15:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! You said that you were gonna conquer the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.82,0:15:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We really believed in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.96,0:15:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.03,0:15:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.07,0:15:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.07,0:15:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Buggy wanted to show us\Nhow to save our frozen mates!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.11,0:15:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,With his frozen body? How great he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.71,0:15:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's carry all the other frozen guys to the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.75,0:15:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.58,0:15:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.19,0:15:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow! Save me first, you fools! I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help me, I'm drowning...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.46,0:15:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved our lives how many times now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, you're great! We'll follow you\Nto the end of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.81,0:16:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys! Thank me as much as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.75,0:16:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like I still have my luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.75,0:16:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, where's Mr. 3?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.49,0:16:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The last time we saw Brother 3\Nwas before the barricades came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.02,0:16:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That bastard! He made it out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.13,0:16:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Is this the wall that you're talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The Navy tried to round up the Whitebeards with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.24,0:16:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We're caged birds because of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.44,0:16:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.64,0:16:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Do they really think that they can stop me with this cheap wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.28,0:16:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Navy! Be ready for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't even think that you can get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.72,0:16:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing! To have such conviction after just being defrosted!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.86,0:16:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.40,0:16:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But what should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.93,0:16:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of my way, magma brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.02,0:17:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.05,0:17:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Even you can't win out against the onslaught of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.13,0:17:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.36,0:17:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I was afraid of the most!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.60,0:17:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you telling me to draw their sympathy\Nby putting these on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.40,0:17:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.47,0:17:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have an unguarded moment,\Nyou will lose the fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.51,0:17:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Marco!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't look away like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.16,0:17:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Jozu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.70,0:18:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I be the last voice you hear before you die?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.44,0:18:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.98,0:18:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Pops is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.18,0:18:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.32,0:18:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! It's too late for you to go out now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.36,0:18:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Koby, there's no question! It's obviously the Navy's victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.19,0:18:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Red Hound-san got Whitebeard
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.36,0:18:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and Yellow Monkey-san and Blue Pheasant-san got Marco
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.40,0:18:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and Jozu, 1st and 3rd division commanders!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And Straw Hat can't fight anymore after getting beaten up so bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.01,0:18:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the best they can do against all the forces of the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.85,0:18:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be much much stronger and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.82,0:18:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll become a Navy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.35,0:18:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...ad...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.32,0:19:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...admiral someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.42,0:19:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Oh, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.46,0:19:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I-I'm sorry! I got carried away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.13,0:19:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's embarrassing! I wanna crawl in a hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,After I met you, I became emboldened a little bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.54,0:19:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Koby!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.21,0:19:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna fight me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.31,0:19:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, of course you have to become such a heavy hitter!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.71,0:19:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, it was just a pipe dream for me to become an admiral!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.32,0:19:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Luffy-san's strength gave out before he accomplished his goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.16,0:19:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible for me because all I do is run despite being a Navy soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.10,0:19:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.77,0:19:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over already! So let's just sit back\Nand enjoy it from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.10,0:19:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, Koby?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.94,0:19:56.41,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,Are you asking me\Nto inject another shot of Energy Hormone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.41,0:19:58.28,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,That's insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.88,0:20:04.09,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,You gotta stop it now!\NYou've been fighting since Impel Down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.09,0:20:07.89,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,You got poisoned and you were almost killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.89,0:20:10.29,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,You're pushing it too far already!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.16,0:20:17.50,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,Like I said before, Energy Hormone\Nis nothing more than a temporary treatment!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.50,0:20:22.67,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,If you just keep using it,\Nyou will die for sure afterwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'd be able to do all I could...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.85,0:20:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be happy to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.99,0:20:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me fight, Iva-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.00,0:20:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops got beaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.67,0:20:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Marco! Jozu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.44,0:20:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can't fight now
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.44,0:20:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and if I can't rescue Ace, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.15,0:21:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather take my own life afterwards!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.78,0:21:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me have the strength to fight for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.04,0:21:35.58,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,I said I can't! If I let you die now, I'd be too ashamed to face Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.58,0:21:38.01,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,You hardheaded fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.52,0:21:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the other guy?! What's taking him so long?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.19,0:21:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Since it was such short notice,\Nhe's having trouble getting ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.06,0:21:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.57,0:21:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.94,0:22:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.68,0:22:08.28,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.42,0:22:16.39,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,Do whatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.36,0:22:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing to Straw Hat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.77,0:22:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Straw Hat is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.78,0:22:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way! I thought he received a mortal wound by getting kicked
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.65,0:22:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,in the teeth by Yellow Monkey-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.49,0:22:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! Where are you going?! It's too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.59,0:23:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Koby...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.50,0:23:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.97,0:23:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.24,0:23:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.35,0:23:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Using Ivankov's Energy Hormone,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.12,0:23:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy works up the last\Nof his strength and runs forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.82,0:23:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Navy forces form a massive wall in his path.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.39,0:23:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Among them stands one young man\Ntrying to motivate himself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.26,0:23:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,to achieve the heights he once swore to reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.97,0:23:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.17,0:23:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,"To Live Up to a Promise!!\NLuffy and Koby Collide!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.27,0:23:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
